---
/**
 * Security Page
 */

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Security"
  description="DigiHoof security practices. Learn how we protect your hoof radiograph data and reports with secure cloud infrastructure."
>

<section class="split-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Security</h1>

    <h2>Secure Cloud Infrastructure</h2>
    <p>
      DigiHoof operates on secure cloud infrastructure designed for reliability and scalability,
      ensuring your hoof radiograph data and reports are protected.
    </p>

    <h2>Encryption</h2>
    <p>
      All data is encrypted in transit using HTTPS protocols.
    </p>

    <h2>Access Control</h2>
    <p>
      Access to reports and imaging data is protected by authentication controls
      and permission-based user management.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Redundancy</h2>
    <p>
      Data is stored with redundancy safeguards to reduce risk of loss.
    </p>

    <h2>Secure Report Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      Shared hoof radiograph reports use secure access mechanisms
      that allow controlled viewing by farriers and collaborators
      without exposing the full clinic account.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
